-- Jeter Breaks Ankle in Yankees 6-4 MLB Playoff Loss to Tigers
-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 2012-10-14T05:41:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-14/jeter-breaks-ankle-in-yankees-6-4-mlb-playoff-loss-to-tigers.html
New York Yankees shortstop  Derek
Jeter  broke his left ankle in the 12th inning of the team’s 6-4
Game 1 playoff loss to the Detroit Tigers.  Game 2 of baseball’s best-of-seven American League
Championship Series will be held later today at Yankee Stadium.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nancy Kercheval in Washington at 
